article_node.title: Tracee Ellis Ross Reveals TSA Pulled a 'Private' Rechargeable Item Out of Her Bag at Security
article_node.summary: Tracee Ellis Ross recounted an awkward TSA screening on the August 15 episode of Jimmy Kimmel Live, when agents opened her carry‑on and found a rechargeable bedside item she had kept in line with airline rules. She used the moment to promote her new Roku Channel series, Solo Traveling, and shared how her solo‑traveling reputation has grown into a dedicated following. The article also highlights Southwest Airlines’ May 28 restriction on portable batteries in bags and includes guest host Nicole Byer’s own airport mishaps and travel‑packing tips.
